Class MagicBox

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
IDevice, IInputOutput
public class MagicBox
extends DriverStation

This class will make it easier to access the digital and analog inputs of the Cypress board. They are accessed through DriverStation.getDigital/AnalogInput This class should be used as a helper for a particular robot's magic box.
